      "input": {
        "tier": "DOMAIN",
        "title": "Powerhouse Platforms",
        "createdAt": "2026-03-30T19:20:00.000Z",
        "description": "Two complementary platforms: Decentralized Operations (coordination engine) and Builder (reusable module creation with value sharing).",
        "orientation": "Powerhouse provides two complementary platforms that form the digital substrate of the SNO model. The Decentralized Operations Platform is the coordination engine \u2014 it structures daily operations through programmable, rule-based processes for compensation, budgeting, IP management, and contributor reputation, generating verifiable records that serve as shared source of truth. The Builder Platform governs creation \u2014 contributors define document types, schemas, automation rules, and interfaces as reusable modules published to a shared registry, where usage generates revenue for original authors. Together they encode governance logic, collaboration structures, and incentive mechanisms directly into software. The Operations Platform stabilizes work; the Builder Platform opens innovation. Neither is a product to sell \u2014 they are foundational infrastructure for post-corporate organizations."
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:49.000Z"
    }
  },
